{"tid":1103131,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔開心到唔想做人","createTime":"2019-04-12T07:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T07:11:47.000Z","uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd9324b4ec16ea4a22c805a5db07d13f5fc7837","tid":1103131,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4659664d6d32a50ad7d533b3d8a26d304dbcd9db","tid":1103131,"uid":54737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd9324b4ec16ea4a22c805a5db07d13f5fc7837","tid":1103131,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"吃個火鍋先啦"},{"pid":"ce36bd7ac08393072041318c576c3e4f297bc54f","tid":1103131,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5cd9324b4ec16ea4a22c805a5db07d13f5fc7837","tid":1103131,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8NqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=8b6df366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"915c5102140530df87b6c0670069a860711d2e9d","tid":1103131,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"直接連登講咩事，大把ching幫你諗計"}]}